	<b><font color="#FCC504">How do I test my signature?</font></b><br />
<br />
Please do not post a thread entitled Sig Test, since images use up a lot of resources. Post a reply to any subject containing your signature, but instead of hitting Submit Reply, press the Preview Reply button and voila: you can see how your sig will look without spamming the forums.<br /></font></td>
